OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775229064
OL,3,CUrgent Treatment Centre in Cumbria
OL,4,Ccloses for two days due to staffing
OL,5,Cgaps
OL,7,FKeswick's Urgent Treatment Centre is
OL,8,Fclosed today (1st April ) and tomorrow
OL,9,F(2nd April) due to "unexpected staff
OL,10,Fabsence".
OL,12,FJust last month bosses at the North
OL,13,FCumbria Integrated Care NHS Foundation
OL,14,FTrust - the body overseeing the UTC -
OL,15,Fsaid they were committed to improving
OL,16,Fthe site.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
