FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775229064
OL,3,CUrgent Treatment Centre in Cumbria
OL,4,Ccloses for two days due to staffing
OL,5,Cgaps
OL,7,FToday a post from the trust said: "We
OL,8,Fhave explored a number of options to
OL,9,Ftry and cover these gaps in staffing,
OL,10,Fhowever due to the upcoming resident
OL,11,Fdoctor industrial action our emergency
OL,12,Fand urgent care staff are already
OL,13,Fworking additional shifts and this has
OL,14,Fnot been possible.
OL,16,F"We are doing everything we can to
OL,17,Fminimise disruption to the service,
OL,18,Fhowever there may be further closures
OL,19,Fover Easter, and we will keep you
OL,20,Fupdated."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775229064
OL,3,CUrgent Treatment Centre in Cumbria
OL,4,Ccloses for two days due to staffing
OL,5,Cgaps
OL,7,FWhilst the UTC in Keswick is closed,
OL,8,FPenrith's remains open, alongside the
OL,9,FA&E Departments at the Cumberland
OL,10,FInfirmary and West Cumberland Hospital.
OL,12,FLast month the trust said they'd
OL,13,F"restated its commitment to the future
OL,14,Fof Keswick and Penrith Urgent
OL,15,FTreatment Centres."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
