PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1775229064
OL,3,CUrgent Treatment Centre in Cumbria
OL,4,Ccloses for two days due to staffing
OL,5,Cgaps
OL,7,FDr Gill Findley, Executive Chief Nurse
OL,8,Fsaid in March: "We know how valuable
OL,9,Fthe service is for the community and
OL,10,Fthe tourist population in the heart of
OL,11,Fthe Lake District, and the Trust is
OL,12,Fcommitted to maintaining the service
OL,13,Fwe have at both hospitals.
OL,15,F"The Urgent Treatment Centre offers a
OL,16,Ffantastic service to our population.
OL,17,FIt performs consistently well
OL,18,Fachieving above 95% for seeing
OL,19,Fpatients within the four-hour standard
OL,20,Fand we regularly receive compliments
OL,21,Ffor the service."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
